{
  "stem": "10406.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was somebody married, a person like that, who lived in the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a young man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- again, it was his luck to walk on my street, like, one house away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And suddenly I saw this German soldier with his rifle butt, you know, hitting that man over the head.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the man collapsed, cursing at him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And eventually the soldier left, and he managed to get up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he only lived, like, a block away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw the way he was walking, like, he was having trouble.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He made it back to his house, and he died the next day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it just didn't happen suddenly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So now, you know, it's a process.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next thing that happens is that we-- somehow we get the feeling that something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was-- that was in the beginning of '42.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so at that point, we thought it was serious, so my mother, my sister, my brother, and I went to our grandparents' house, my father's parents' house, and they made a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on-- it was on one of the streets going from-- from [POLISH] to [POLISH], and it was, like, a little bit out of the city already.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, like, in a suburb area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were probably the only Jewish house at that particular spot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they made a hiding place in an attic, and when we got there, everybody got up in the attic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That consisted of three of my aunts, my father's sisters, my sister, and my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my grandfather was very old and sick, and at that point, they still didn't-- sort of theoretically didn't-- take older men and young children.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
